---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <h1>Projects</h1>

      <p>These are the ideas, books, systems, and experiments I am building through Journey to Greatness.</p>

      <h2>There's Two Boats</h2>
      <p>A historical book project exploring hidden Black history, lost choices, survival, power, and legacy.</p>

      <h2>Universal Mechanics</h2>
      <p>A personal framework for studying systems, science, reality, and how the world connects.</p>

      <h2>NYC Pavement Digital Twin</h2>
      <p>A project focused on predicting street failure using traffic, salt, water, utility cuts, and pavement conditions.</p>

      <h2>AI Comic-to-Movie System</h2>
      <p>A future tool idea for turning comics, books, and stories into animated AI video experiences.</p>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
